      <title>中国工厂不愿支付创纪录的铜价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/chinese-factories-recoil-from-paying-record-copper-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于客户对更昂贵的产品退缩，中国工厂不愿支付创纪录的铜价，推迟了金属订单并削减了产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/chinese-factories-recoil-from-paying-record-copper-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 02:03:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
